https://leetcode.com/problems/power-of-two/
--------------------------
Power of 2 => x & -x  == x or x & (x - 1) == 0
(*) -x will revert all bits except the rightmost 1-bit. E.g. 10100 => 01100
(*) x & (x-1) sets right most bit to zero
https://leetcode.com/problems/number-of-1-bits/
----
(*) n&1 = get the right most bit
(*) ((n >> i) & 1)  == 1 check if ith bit is set to 1

https://leetcode.com/problems/reverse-bits/
----
